e":"2017-11-16T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"張柏芝"},{"pid":"d19aa58b57387b82b64480bc683db63ea47ce576","tid":469911,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似早前中大在1997年出左個報告<br />\n話驗到懷孕婦女的血液中有男性的基因<br />\n結果被人惡搞成先父遺傳證據<br />\n<br />\n醫學界後來否定左先父遺傳。<br />\n<br />\n不過就用左呢個發現，發展左 T21 和 Nifty 技術。Nifty [非侵入性胎兒染色體基因檢測（英语：Non- Invasive Fetal Trisomy Test] 。用抽血方式，來檢驗嬰兒基因疾病的醫學檢測法。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/23704707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F23704707&d=vAfC9Q9YMLRu6Awf%2Fp1NvMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=30fdf4a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/23704707</a>"},{"pid":"922ccc3353bbfc3e6438a7906b242cdadac4d412","tid":469911,"uid":106375,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"如果係真既話俾n個男人中出過既女人有好多唔同dna 生出黎個仔實無敵又少遺傳病"},{"pid":"c5864b5bfaa1076f5a49f1ba50df9b2e5e9e9ce5","tid":469911,"uid":14739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"吳x 希"},{"pid":"e957e01df999030e8bc4356c1188c5fe6cf6faee","tid":469911,"uid":61484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"睇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297b91b1705f4931a5ca4d1114b9c20a68c34c2b","tid":469911,"uid":96218,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"你由班on9宣傳下佢地個處女情意結啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實世界冇人會聽佢地噏 當就下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b32fa6145e03176b0e15a9030bb0648e979d9b3","tid":469911,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:59:32.000Z","msg":"細眼扁鼻黃種女俾n手白鬼佬屌過，之後同細眼扁鼻黃種人生仔會點"},{"pid":"22b77e604ded1faa4d83656ad368cc0cbb8f38dd","tid"